node.text: We’re so excited about the latest additions to our partnership with the talented @susanconnor_ny. Crafted through her own proprietary print engraving process in her Brooklyn Studio, these textiles have an awe-inspiring level of detail that’s become her signature. We’re so in love with how beautifully each of these pieces turned out and can’t wait for you to get your hands on them. ✨
